=== [ topic ][ pre ] ===
[ --- start ---- ]
- <pre> = pre-format
- white space, tabs, new-line will be preserved and not ignored
<pre>public class Hello {
   public static void main(String[] args) {
      System.out.println("Hello");
   }
}</pre>

produces:

public class Hello {
   public static void main(String[] args) {
      System.out.println("Hello");
   }
}
[ ---  end  ---- ]

